column4: Made of 100% cotton these Newport towels have shades of blue, green, beige and cream stripes. Sold as a set of two.
This metal rack contains 5 hooks for hanging your favorite items has a aged ivory metal that is wired wrapped with decorative ends.
This Burlap pillow is natural color burlap with cream ruffles on all sides and 3 burlap and cream posies.
